{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3825,"text":"I'm an Iranian-American Muslim female,"},{"time":6167,"text":"like all of you."},{"time":7455,"text":"And I'm also a social justice comedian,"},{"time":9788,"text":"something that I insist is an actual job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12127,"text":"To explain what that is,\nlet me tell you how I got here."},{"time":14818,"text":"I've performed all over the country."},{"time":16597,"text":"And let me tell you,\nAmerica is majestic, right?"},{"time":18918,"text":"It's got breathtaking nature,"},{"time":20667,"text":"waffle houses"},{"time":21841,"text":"and diabetes as far as the eye can see."},{"time":23848,"text":"It is really something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25784,"text":"Now, the American population\ncan be broken up"},{"time":28047,"text":"into three main categories:"},{"time":29612,"text":"there's mostly wonderful people,"},{"time":31374,"text":"haters"},{"time":32549,"text":"and Florida."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33724,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":35331,"text":"Besides Florida, the most troubling\ncategory here are the Haters."},{"time":38669,"text":"They are a minority,"},{"time":40882,"text":"but they overcompensate\nby being extra loud."},{"time":43409,"text":"They have the Napoleon complex\nof demographics,"},{"time":45742,"text":"and yes, some of the men do wear heels."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47834,"text":"As a social justice comedian,"},{"time":49961,"text":"it's my goal to convert these haters,"},{"time":51853,"text":"because they hate a lot of things,\nwhich leads to negative outcomes,"},{"time":55083,"text":"like racism, violence and Ted Nugent."},{"time":59400,"text":"This is not an exhaustive list;"},{"time":61306,"text":"I'm probably missing 3-7 items."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63004,"text":"But the point is,"},{"time":64250,"text":"we have to reckon with the haters."},{"time":66003,"text":"But there's variance within this group"},{"time":67838,"text":"and it's not efficient to go\nafter all of them, right?"},{"time":70883,"text":"So what I've done is created\na highly scientific Taxonomy of Haters."},{"time":74420,"text":"I basically took all of the haters,"},{"time":76167,"text":"I put them in a petri dish,\nlike a scientist,"},{"time":79037,"text":"and this is what I found."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":81695,"text":"First off, we have the trolls."},{"time":84013,"text":"These are your garden-variety\ndigital haters."},{"time":86420,"text":"They're the people who quit their jobs"},{"time":88310,"text":"so they can post on YouTube\nvideos all day long."},{"time":91448,"text":"There's also the drive-by haters."},{"time":94133,"text":"Now, these people will be at a stoplight,"},{"time":96449,"text":"they'll wait for the light to turn green"},{"time":98442,"text":"and when it does, they yell,\n\"Go back to your own country!\""},{"time":101288,"text":"Now back in the day, they would've\nactually gotten out of their cars"},{"time":104529,"text":"and hated you to your face."},{"time":105845,"text":"But they just don't make them\nlike they used to --"},{"time":108247,"text":"which is another sign\nof the decline in America."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110556,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":112293,"text":"The next category"},{"time":113468,"text":"is the mission-oriented-bigot-\nwhose-group-affiliation-"},{"time":116135,"text":"gives-them-cover-for-hating hater."},{"time":117827,"text":"These guys like to hate\nvia a seemingly nice organization,"},{"time":121389,"text":"like a church or a nonprofit,"},{"time":123586,"text":"and they oftentimes like to speak\nin an old-timey voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126324,"text":"But the group I'm most\ninterested in is the swing hater."},{"time":130888,"text":"The swing hater is sister\nto the swing voter --"},{"time":134499,"text":"they just can't decide!"},{"time":136252,"text":"They're like ideological sluts"},{"time":138154,"text":"who move from hating to not hating."},{"time":140168,"text":"And they do it because they don't have\nenough information."},{"time":142947,"text":"This is the group I like to target\nwith social justice comedy."},{"time":145949,"text":"Why comedy?"},{"time":147283,"text":"Because on a scale of comedy to brochure,"},{"time":149836,"text":"the average American prefers comedy,\nas you can see from this graph."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153558,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":154733,"text":"Comedy is very popular."},{"time":156117,"text":"And by the way,"},{"time":157292,"text":"this is a mathematically accurate graph,"},{"time":159262,"text":"generated from fake numbers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160810,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162311,"text":"Now, the question is:"},{"time":163520,"text":"Why does social justice comedy work?"},{"time":166329,"text":"Because, first off, it makes you laugh."},{"time":169052,"text":"And when you're laughing,\nyou enter into a state of openness."},{"time":172238,"text":"And in that moment of openness,"},{"time":173820,"text":"a good social justice comedian\ncan stick in a whole bunch of information,"},{"time":177508,"text":"and if they're really skilled,"},{"time":179062,"text":"a rectal exam."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180237,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":182794,"text":"Here are some ground rules\nfor social justice comedy:"},{"time":186019,"text":"first off, it's not partisan."},{"time":188002,"text":"This isn't political comedy,\nthis is about justice,"},{"time":190567,"text":"and no one is against justice."},{"time":192288,"text":"Two, it's inviting and warm,"},{"time":194305,"text":"it makes you feel like you're sitting\ninside of a burrito."},{"time":197090,"text":"Three, it's funny but sneaky,"},{"time":199519,"text":"like you could be hearing\nan interesting treatise"},{"time":202339,"text":"on income inequality,"},{"time":203577,"text":"that's encased in a really\nsophisticated poop joke."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206515,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":208158,"text":"Here's how I see\nsocial justice comedy working."},{"time":211205,"text":"A few years ago, I rounded up a bunch\nof Muslim-American comedians --"},{"time":214527,"text":"in a non-violent way --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":215717,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217265,"text":"And we went around the country"},{"time":218761,"text":"to places like Alabama, Arizona,\nTennessee, Georgia --"},{"time":221722,"text":"places where they love the Muzzies --"},{"time":223945,"text":"and we did stand-up shows."},{"time":226657,"text":"We called the tour\n\"The Muslims Are Coming!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":228995,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":231284,"text":"We turned this into a movie,"},{"time":233014,"text":"and then after the movie came out,"},{"time":235262,"text":"a known hate group spent 300,000 dollars"},{"time":238689,"text":"on an anti-Muslim poster campaign"},{"time":240834,"text":"with the MTA -- that's\nthe New York City subway system."},{"time":243729,"text":"Now, the posters were truly offensive,"},{"time":245599,"text":"not to mentioned poorly designed --"},{"time":247384,"text":"I mean, if you're going to be bigoted,"},{"time":249242,"text":"you might as well use a better font."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251018,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":252043,"text":"But we decided, why not launch\nour own poster campaign"},{"time":256019,"text":"that says nice things about Muslims,"},{"time":257917,"text":"while promoting the movie."},{"time":259188,"text":"So myself and fellow comedian\nDean Obeidallah"},{"time":261337,"text":"decided to launch the fighting-bigotry-\nwith-delightful-posters campaign."},{"time":264857,"text":"We raised the money, worked\nwith the MTA for over 5 months,"},{"time":268631,"text":"got the posters approved,"},{"time":269966,"text":"and two days after they\nwere supposed to go up,"},{"time":272869,"text":"the MTA decided to ban the posters,"},{"time":276040,"text":"citing political content."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277900,"text":"Let's take a look\nat a couple of those posters."},{"time":280157,"text":"Here's one."},{"time":281475,"text":"Facts about Muslims:"},{"time":282713,"text":"Muslims invented\nthe concept of a hospital."},{"time":284834,"text":"OK."},{"time":286009,"text":"Fact: Grown-up Muslims can do\nmore push-ups than baby Muslims."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291603,"text":"Fact: Muslims invented Justin Timberlake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294475,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":295578,"text":"Let's take a look at another one."},{"time":297484,"text":"The ugly truth about Muslims:"},{"time":298937,"text":"they have great frittata recipes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301549,"text":"Now clearly, frittatas are considered\npolitical by the MTA."},{"time":306080,"text":"Either that, or the mere mention\nof Muslims in a positive light"},{"time":309561,"text":"was considered political -- but it isn't."},{"time":311609,"text":"It's about justice."},{"time":312886,"text":"So we decided to change"},{"time":314069,"text":"our fighting-bigortry-\nwith-delightful-posters campaign"},{"time":316701,"text":"and turn it into the fighting-bigotry-\nwith-a-delightful-lawsuit campaign."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320224,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":321863,"text":"So basically, what I'm saying\nis a couple of dirt-bag comedians"},{"time":324851,"text":"took on a major New York City agency"},{"time":327406,"text":"and the comedians won."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328970,"text":"(Applause and cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":331570,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":332745,"text":"Victory was a very weird feeling."},{"time":334492,"text":"I was like, \"Is this what\nblonde girls feel like all the time?"},{"time":337452,"text":"'Cause this is amazing!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":338795,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341702,"text":"Here's another example."},{"time":343999,"text":"I'm asked everywhere I go:\n\"Why don't Muslims denounce terrorism?\""},{"time":347252,"text":"We do. But OK, I'll take the bait."},{"time":349467,"text":"So I decided to launch\nthedailydenouncer.com."},{"time":352137,"text":"It's a website that denounces\nterrorism every day of the week,"},{"time":355121,"text":"while taking the weekends off."},{"time":356626,"text":"Let's take a look at an example."},{"time":359008,"text":"They generally appear\nas single-panel cartoons,"},{"time":361429,"text":"\"I denounce terrorism! I also denounce\npeople who never fill the paper tray!\""},{"time":365872,"text":"The point of the website\nis that it denounces terrorism"},{"time":368711,"text":"while recognizing that it's ridiculous"},{"time":370871,"text":"that we have to constantly\ndenounce terrorism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373656,"text":"But if bigotry isn't your thing,"},{"time":375931,"text":"social justice comedy is useful\nfor all sorts of issues."},{"time":379346,"text":"For example, myself and fellow\ncomedian Lee Camp"},{"time":382261,"text":"went to the Cayman Islands\nto investigate offshore banking."},{"time":385750,"text":"Now, the United States loses\nsomething like 300 billion dollars a year"},{"time":390679,"text":"in these offshore tax havens."},{"time":392528,"text":"Not to brag,"},{"time":393806,"text":"but at the end of every month,"},{"time":395298,"text":"I have something like 5-15 dollars\nin disposable income."},{"time":397966,"text":"So we walked into these banks\nin the Cayman Islands"},{"time":400462,"text":"and asked if we could\nopen up a bank account"},{"time":402642,"text":"with eight dollars and 27 cents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404712,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406539,"text":"The bank managers would indulge us\nfor 30-45 seconds before calling security."},{"time":411994,"text":"Security would come out,\nbrandish their weapons,"},{"time":414590,"text":"and then we would squeal\nwith fear and run away,"},{"time":417384,"text":"because -- and this is the last\nrule of social justice comedy --"},{"time":420437,"text":"sometimes it makes you want\nto take a dump in your pants."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423175,"text":"Most of my work is meant to be fun."},{"time":426046,"text":"It's meant to generate\na connection and laughter."},{"time":429157,"text":"But yes, sometimes I get\nrun off the grounds by security."},{"time":432513,"text":"Sometimes I get mean tweets and hate mail."},{"time":435504,"text":"Sometimes I get voice mails saying\nthat if I continue telling my jokes,"},{"time":440403,"text":"they'll kill me\nand they'll kill my family."},{"time":443489,"text":"And those death threats\nare definitely not funny."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447287,"text":"But despite the occasional danger,"},{"time":449445,"text":"I still think that social justice comedy\nis one of our best weapons."},{"time":453369,"text":"I mean, we've tried\na lot of approaches to social justice,"},{"time":456448,"text":"like war and competitive ice dancing."},{"time":458994,"text":"But still, a lot of things\nare still kind of awful."},{"time":463265,"text":"So I think it's time we try and tell\na really good poop joke."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467033,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468208,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}